            <a href="#">Audio & Streaming <i class="fa-solid fa-angle-down"></i></a>
            <a href="#">Networking</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero container">
        <div class="hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-text fade-up">
                <h1>Level Up Your <br><span>Digital Arsenal</span></h1>
                <p>Equip yourself with elite performance hardware. From next-gen GPUs to professional studio audio gear.
                </p>
                <a href="#" class="btn-pill">Explore Gear <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"
